  "title": "ISic001412. I.Sicily inscription 001412",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Ἐπὶ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">Ἐπὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἱερομνάμονος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ἱερομνάμονος</span>  <span data-text=\"Σαννίωνος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">Σα[ν]νίω[νος]</span>  <span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">[τοῦ]</span>  <span data-text=\"δεῖνα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">[δεῖνα]</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἀγωνοθετᾶν\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">ἀγωνοθετᾶν</span>  <span data-text=\"Κλεάνδρου\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">Κλεάνδρου</span>  <span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">τοῦ</span>  <span data-text=\"Αρ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">Αρ</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"Παρμ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">Παρμ</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"\">τοῦ</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Ζωίλου\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"\">Ζωίλου</span>  <span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">τοῦ</span>  <span data-text=\"Θέστωνος\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"\">Θέστ[ωνος?</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"λαμπαδισταὶ\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"\">λαμπαδιστ[αὶ</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Ἐπὶ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ΕΠΙ</span><span data-text=\"ἱερομνάμονος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ΙΕΡΟΜΝΑΜΟΝΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Σαννίωνος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">ΣΑ[.]ΝΙΩ[...</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">...</span><span data-text=\"δεῖνα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">.....]</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἀγωνοθετᾶν\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">ΑΓΩΝΟΘΕΤΑΝ</span><span data-text=\"Κλεάνδρου\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">ΚΛΕΑΝΔΡΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">ΤΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"Αρ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">ΑΡ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"Παρμ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">ΠΑΡΜ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"\">...</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Ζωίλου\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"\">ΖΩΙΛΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">ΤΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"Θέστωνος\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"\">ΘΕΣΤ[....</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"λαμπαδισταὶ\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"\">ΛΑΜΠΑΔΙΣΤ[..</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001412_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo della cultura e delle Arti Figurative Bizantine e Normanne\" src=\"ISic001412_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001412.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo della cultura e delle Arti Figurative Bizantine e Normanne\" src=\"ISic001412-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001412_leftthreequarter_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo della cultura e delle Arti Figurative Bizantine e Normanne\" src=\"ISic001412_leftthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001412_leftthreequarter.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo della cultura e delle Arti Figurative Bizantine e Normanne\" src=\"ISic001412_leftthreequarter-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001412_rightthreequarter_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo della cultura e delle Arti Figurative Bizantine e Normanne\" src=\"ISic001412_rightthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001412_rightthreequarter.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo della cultura e delle Arti Figurative Bizantine e Normanne\" src=\"ISic001412_rightthreequarter-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Manganaro 1999</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>One of two inscr. on this block. The other inscription <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic002937\" target=\"_blank\">ISic002937</a> on the top surface appears approximately contemporary and is also apparently of gymnasial relevance. The text requires minor revision in light of further autopsy</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 49.1271 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 46.1242a <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 26.1060 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1965 202 tav.73.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841</a>  </li><li> Cordiano 1997 43-45 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002064\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002064</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1999 65 no.55 fig.137 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Letters of the mid-Hellenistic period: epsilon has short middle bar; omicron is small and mid-line; mu has vertical first and last strokes, the mid-point descends half-way; alpha is formed with both broken and straight bar; sigma has approximately parallel top and bottom strokes; omega is open; theta formed with a central point.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ι type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Λ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Λ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Π type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Π type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2.1</a> </p> Line 1-5  13-15  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
